<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bowser Jr. - Daggerheart Leader</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #1a1a1a; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 40px; }
        .card { width: 450px; background: #fff; border: 6px solid #e74c3c; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); overflow: hidden; }
        
        /* IMAGE SECTION */
        .portrait { width: 100%; height: 250px; background: #333; overflow: hidden; position: relative; border-bottom: 4px solid #e74c3c; }
        .portrait img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .portrait-label { position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: 0; background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; border-top-left-radius: 10px; }

        .header { background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 15px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .stats-bar { display: flex; justify-content: space-around; background: #c0392b; color: white; padding: 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; }
        .content { padding: 20px; color: #2c3e50; }
        .section-title { font-weight: 800; border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c; margin: 15px 0 8px; color: #c0392b; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .ability { margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
        .ability strong { color: #000; font-weight: 700; }
        .fury { background: #fff5f5; border: 1px dashed #e74c3c; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 15px; }
        .tier { font-size: 11px; text-align: center; color: #95a5a6; margin-top: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <div class="portrait">
        <img src="YOUR_IMAGE_HERE.jpg" alt="Bowser Jr. AI Image">
        <div class="portrait-label">Leader Adversary</div>
    </div>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Bowser Jr.</h1>
        <span>The Heir to the Koopa Throne</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="stats-bar">
        <span>HP: 12</span>
        <span>EVASION: 12</span>
        <span>ARMOR: 4</span>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="section-title">Standard Actions</div>
        <div class="ability">
            <strong>Shadow Mario Brush:</strong> Bowser Jr. lashes out. Success deals 8 physical damage and coats the target in paint. Painted targets have <em>Disadvantage</em> on their next Agility roll.
        </div>
        <div class="ability">
            <strong>Clown Car Drill:</strong> Bowser Jr. charges. Deals 12 physical damage and pushes the target back one zone.
        </div>

        <div class="section-title">Leader & Fear Actions</div>
        <div class="ability">
            <strong>"Dad Said It's My Turn!":</strong> (Spend 1 Fear) Bowser Jr. forces a nearby minion to take a hit for him, transferring the damage of one successful attack to an adjacent ally.
        </div>

        <div class="fury">
            <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 0; border-color: #000;">Fury Mode: Shell Spin</div>
            <div class="ability">
                <em>Triggers when at 6 HP or less.</em> Bowser Jr. retreats into his shell. His <strong>Armor increases to 6</strong>, but he can only use the <strong>Shell Spin</strong> action (Hits everyone in Melee range for 10 damage).
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tier">Tier 2 Adversary • Daggerheart Homebrew</div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
